sub_title: Head of Sales & Marketing Recruitment | Connecting senior Sales & Marketing talent with innovative FinTechs worldwide | Storm2
summary:
⚡️ ‎Our Story

Storm2’s mission is to be the global market leader in connecting rapid growth FinTech companies with experienced & technically outstanding individuals. Launched in 2019 by executives from a hugely successful global recruitment company, we've already partnered with hundreds of FinTech companies across the globe, to support them in finding the talent to achieve their mission.
 
🚀 Why We're The Market Leader in Connecting FinTech Talent 

We’re able to connect the best talent in FinTech by continually networking with both highly skilled professionals and innovative clients.

𝗤𝘂𝗮𝗹𝗶𝘁𝘆 - Our database of ~200,000 FinTech specific individuals ensures we connect the best and brightest minds in the market
𝗦𝗽𝗲𝗲𝗱 - Our deep FinTech network allows us to connect talent within 72 hours of activating a search
𝗗𝗲𝗹𝗶𝘃𝗲𝗿𝘆 - Proven with over 100 FinTech companies, our commitment to you is that we'll deliver on what we promise 

⭐️ Who We Recruit

𝗣𝗿𝗼𝗱𝘂𝗰𝘁 – CPO, Lead Product manager, Senior Product Designer
𝗘𝗻𝗴𝗶𝗻𝗲𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗴 – CTO, Head of Engineering, DevOps, Infrastructure, Full Stack, Data
𝗖𝗼𝗺𝗺𝗲𝗿𝗰𝗶𝗮𝗹 – CCO, Head of Sales, Head of Partnership, Commercial Director
𝗙𝗶𝗻𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲 & 𝗢𝗽𝗲𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻𝘀 – CFO, COO, Head of Treasury, Senior Financial Accountant
𝗥𝗶𝘀𝗸 & 𝗖𝗼𝗺𝗽𝗹𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲 – CRO, Head of Compliance, Head of AML

🌎 Where We Recruit
Europe, Asia & North America

📧 Get in Touch
